          <p><italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="73baf34e-5113-4951-b89a-58fefa3be59a" obkms_process="TRUE"><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Gaura</tp:taxon-name-part><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">hispida</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Bentham, Pl. Hartw. 288. 1840.</p>
